------------------------------
Surf_buck-ed_up (#3 in the BUCK series)
Map created by Buck Nasty
------------------------------

- Kill style arena type map
- Bombsite is disable for the first minute
- Buyzone is located at the bombsite
- The bullseye pads shoot you up in the air
- Jail opens every 30 seconds for ~2 seconds
- Guns: AK-47, AUG, G3SG1, M3, M4A1, MP5NAVY, P-90, SCOUT, SG552, UMP45

- Map on the cycle @ 72.68.154.90:30000
- Join my steam group http://steamcommunity.com/groups/bucknastysurf

- There shouldn't be bugs, errors, nothing with this map. I had 2 open betas on my server so it's good to go.

- Comments/compliments are always welcome, including constructive criticism! (but i won't use the constructive crti. cause this map is final)

Enjoy!
--Buck Nasty

http://solidsurf.info/
